:: Avery Valentines Chocolate
<<effects>><<wearProp "valentines chocolate">>
<<earnFeat "Be My Valentine">>
You take out the box of Valentine's Day chocolate you made, and hold it out to Avery.
<br><br>
Avery raises an eyebrow. "What's this?" <<he>> asks as <<he>> takes it, lifting the lid.
<br><br>
<<if $speech_attitude is "meek" or $speech_attitude_avery>>
	"I made you some chocolate for Valentine's Day," you say without making eye contact.
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"Valentine's Day chocolate. Made it myself."
<<else>>
	"I made you some chocolate." You smile. "It's Valentine's Day, after all."
<</if>>
<br><br>
You watch as Avery plucks one of the chocolates from the box, and pushes it into <<his>> mouth. A smile spreads over <<his>> face as <<he>> bites into it.<<npcincr Avery love 1>><<glove>>
<br><br>
"It's delicious," <<he>> says, shutting the box. "I'd eat more, but I don't want to spoil dinner. Thank you, <<pcpetname "Avery">>." <<He>> squeezes your shoulder, then stows the box of chocolates in the back seat of the car.
<br><br>
"Now, shall we go?"
<br><br>
<<link [[Yes|Avery Valentines 2]]>><<endevent>><<set $avery_valentines.done to true>><</link>>
